[b][size=12pt]now to show you how to make a female character[/size][/b]

First go to [b]src>com>rs>game>player[/b] open Appearence.java and look for this

[code=java]        public void female() {[/code]

change it to this.

[code=java]public void female() {
                look[0] = 48; // Hair
                look[1] = 57; // Beard
                look[2] = 57; // Torso
                look[3] = 65; // Arms
                look[4] = 68; // Bracelets
                look[5] = 77; // Legs
                look[6] = 80; // Shoes

                colour[2] = 16;
                colour[1] = 16;
                colour[0] = 3;
                male = false;
        }[/code]

save and exit now go to.

[b]src>com>rs>game>player>content[/b] open commands.java and add this.

[code=java]if (cmd[0].equalsIgnoreCase("female")) {
                player.getAppearence().female();
                                }
if (cmd[0].equalsIgnoreCase("male")) {
                player.getAppearence().male();
                                }[/code]

Were is says....

                look[0] = 48; // Hair
                look[1] = 57; // Beard
                look[2] = 57; // Torso
                look[3] = 65; // Arms
                look[4] = 68; // Bracelets
                look[5] = 77; // Legs
                look[6] = 80; // Shoes

look[0] = 48;//hair this is the hair style so u can look on a 525 or 317 server for different hair styles and u can edit what the character looks like same with beard, torso, arms, bracelets, legs and shoes under it is the skin colour you can also change to what ever you like...

 save exit and compile now your female character will look like this.

