[b][size=12pt]Simple command's help[/size][/b]

So when your adding a new command e.g if its a teleport comamnd and u want it for everyone search in commands.java for this

[code=java]public static boolean processNormalCommand(Player player, String[] cmd,[/code]

past your new command under it so everyone can use it...

Now if you want a admin only command search in commands.java for this... 

[code=java]public static boolean processAdminCommand(final Player player,[/code]

same as above past your code under it save and compile this will help if you ever want to add new command's :D

enjoy post erros ill help asap.
